Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基于大量调查与验证而制作的虚构作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本动画以发生了大地震的首都区为假想舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在动画中 会有部分与实际相出入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原作为追求逼真效果 经过了充分的模拟测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 说话啊悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:02.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵他突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他就这么躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得送他去医院才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:37.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:11.54,title1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,660)\fad(300,0)}「纯白的早晨」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏很不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要什么时候才能帮我们看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经等了很久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会挨个过来看的 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会这样的 不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:25.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问您弟弟有过敏的药物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有过因大病或大伤而住院的记录吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:15.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点帮我们看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请来这边看下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 你不会死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还活蹦乱跳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵才不会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夫 请来这边看下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:57.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命迹象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:58.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意识等级300
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有呼吸和脉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:56.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 姐姐在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来 你很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有乱了阵脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:30.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为悠贵不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:36.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是身体累了 觉得不舒服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:09.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿 姐姐在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:24.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 我睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 才刚刚好就到处乱跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夫说没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系才怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好休息怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是打了点点滴啦 姐姐你太认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不准离开姐姐身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
